S.FORM: I 1966 a miheca saka 7 folad saka 20 a romi'ad masofoc ci Enrique Peña Nieto , malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Mexico anini i ci Enrique Peña Nieto, patirengan a romi'ad i 2012 a miheca saka 12 folad saka 1 a romi'ad.
